high_descs: walk to face shelves with mirror above
pick up dirty tissue on the right side of shelves
wash tissue in sink, remove tissue from sink
turn to face shelves with mirror
place tissue on second shelf from the bottom
anns.task_desc: put a clean tissue onto a shelf

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the bathroom counter to your right.
Pick up the dirty rag on the counter.
With the rag, urn around, walk to the bathroom sink to your left and look down to the sink.
Place the dirty rag inside the sink, wash it, then remove it.
With the clean rag, look up and walk to the counter to your right.
Place the clean rag on the shelf below the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean rag on the shelf below the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go towards the bath tub, then turn right and go towards the door, then turn right and go to the shelf in the corner
Pick up the rag from the top of the shelf
Turn around and make your way to the left side of the sink then turn to the right to face it
Put the rag in the sink and turn on the water then turn off the water and take the rag out of the sink
Turn right then left and make your way back to the shelf in the corner
Put the rag on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned rag on a shelf
